{"tid":2333097,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【Disney+】戰爭機器 (War Machine)或將迎來獨立劇","createTime":"2020-12-20T06:46:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T12:32:57.000Z","uid":318316,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e883856aa7e57f25c2a02b24358f9830704c2d70","tid":2333097,"uid":318316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T06:46:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/f8/31/57/f83157497873161338dc1cfc751bbb55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2Ff8%2F31%2F57%2Ff83157497873161338dc1cfc751bbb55.jpg&h=af2955ac&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n漫威將會宣佈一系列電影（第四階段的信息）與劇集的消息，屆時眾多的電影、劇集計劃將會放出，這對於漫威的影迷來說將會收到許多爆炸性的消息。<br />\n<br />\n而在漫展開始之前，據一名消息人士透露，《戰爭機器》也將計劃拍攝獨立劇集，這位托尼的好基友從鋼鐵俠電影開始就一直活躍在MCU的電影中，也算是一位元老級的人物，如今有希望拍攝個人劇集也讓許多影迷感到欣慰。<br />\n<br />\n戰爭機器（詹姆斯&middot;羅德斯）是一名軍方人員，他的初代戰甲原型是鋼鐵俠的Mark2，後隨着電影劇情的發展也做了許多次的升級，強大的火力是他的戰衣特點。<br />\n<br />\n那麼在《戰爭機器》之前，漫威已經官宣了幾部劇集，前三階段電影中的一些重要人物（像洛基、緋紅女巫、冬兵、幻視、獵鷹）也將迎來自己的獨立劇，加上還未錘定的《鷹眼》，漫威的電視劇到時也將是一場饕鬄盛宴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/entertainment/y3n3rrn.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fentertainment%2Fy3n3rrn.html&d=10CjJG2g6dwwFxaVJa0PIVHO27hz5fVRhbnvZL2FK%2Bg%3D&h=8e48e384\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/entertainment/y3n3rrn.html</a>"},{"pid":"a6a31ba0262ce082db4145e92de9657cc91b591e","tid":2333097,"uid":33869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T06:49:53.000Z","msg":"咪Armor Wars囉"},{"pid":"63c8e08a49fb1c90a7a7ceac7180baf17decac0c","tid":2333097,"uid":35074,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T07:36:22.000Z","msg":"張poster 執到個人 好似猩猩 著住套甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8096a6507c3ef2404df8e59146fcbdfd4d99f3b","tid":2333097,"uid":325309,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T11:31:44.000Z","msg":"我幾鐘